text: "Pressure Down" is a 1986 song by John Farnham and is the second single from his 12th studio album Whispering Jack. It went to number 4 in Australia, number 8 in New Zealand, number 11 in Sweden, number 32 in Germany and number 78 in the United Kingdom. ==References== Category:1986 songs Category:Pop rock songs Category:John Farnham songs
title: Pressure Down
